  <h2>Six Distributed Problems</h2>
  <p class="lead">
    ETDM is a <strong>conditional accelerator</strong> — its benefit depends on whether 
    the problem requires network-wide information propagation.
  </p>

  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">👑</div>
      <h3>Leader Election</h3>
      <p>Max-ID flooding. ETDM shortcuts propagate the max ID faster across the network.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:0.8rem;"><span class="tag tag-green">+12.8% avg improvement</span></p>
    </div>
